languages.text: "Простите великодушно, Ваша Светлость, но нет, не знаем, и выяснять не хотели бы. Кто в здравом уме полезет к неизвестной пакости? Огородили и ладненько!"

"A thousand apologies, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}, but no, we don't, and we'd rather not find out. Who in their right mind would want to get closer to whatever it is? We've contained the foulness — and that's good enough if you ask me!"

languages.text: “万分抱歉，大人，但我们真的不知道，而且我们也不想知道。有哪个头脑正常的人，会想要接近那不知道是什么的东西呢？而且我们已经控制住了污染。要我说，这已经足够了！”

languages.text: «Mil perdones, mi{mf|lord|lady}, pero ni lo sabemos ni queremos saberlo. ¿A quién se le ocurriría querer acercarse más a lo que sea? Hemos contenido esa cosa, ¡y por lo que a mí respecta es suficiente con eso!».
languages.original_text: "A thousand apologies, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}, but no, we don't, and we'd rather not find out. Who in their right mind would want to get closer to whatever it is? We've contained the foulness — and that's good enough if you ask me!"

languages.text: 「陛下、重ね重ね申し訳ないですが、分からないどころか知りたくもありません。まともな人間が、何だアレは近くに行って見てみようと思いますか？汚染物を抑え込んだんです、それで十分じゃないですか！」
languages.original_text: "A thousand apologies, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}, but no, we don't, and we'd rather not find out. Who in their right mind would want to get closer to whatever it is? We've contained the foulness — and that's good enough if you ask me!"

languages.text: "Verzeiht tausendfach, Eure {mf|Lordschaft|Ladyschaft}, aber nein, wir wissen nichts und wollen auch nichts erfahren. Welcher Mensch bei klarem Verstand würde sich der Sache nähern wollen, was immer es sein mag? Wir haben die Fäulnis eingedämmt – und das reicht, wenn Ihr mich fragt!"
languages.original_text: "A thousand apologies, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}, but no, we don't, and we'd rather not find out. Who in their right mind would want to get closer to whatever it is? We've contained the foulness — and that's good enough if you ask me!"

languages.text: « Mille excuses, Votre Seigneurie, mais non, on en sait rien du tout, et c'est aussi bien comme ça. Faudrait plus avoir toute sa tête pour avoir envie d'aller patauger là-dedans ! On a réussi à endiguer cette cochonnerie, et c'est déjà pas mal, si vous voulez mon avis ! »

languages.text: "Affedin {mf|Lord|Leydi} Hazretleri ama hayır, bilmiyoruz. Öğrenmemeyi de yeğleriz. Aklı başında kim böyle ne idiği belirsiz bir şeye yaklaşmak ister ki? Kontrol altına aldık, bana sorarsanız bu kadarı kâfi!"
